  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/45c013a8bb433e3b38d30ad12b003464.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=132 /></span><br>In Red Door Yellow Door, plunge into the depths of your mind, starting with what seems like a normal ritual but quickly revealing its sinister nature. Navigate eerie and haunting environments as you uncover the true essence of this mysterious practice. Confront your deepest fears, solve intricate puzzles, and evade malevolent entities on your quest to find the elusive Red Yellow Door—the only escape from this nightmare. Can you find the door and return to reality, or will you be trapped in the darkness forever?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/beea9c0aa45945c97d1dfc789b62daba.poster.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/beea9c0aa45945c97d1dfc789b62daba.webm?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/beea9c0aa45945c97d1dfc789b62daba.mp4?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f2ed96582c75d05058f4f3ad930f6d67.webp?t=1721570570\" width=283 height=24 /></span><br>Solve intricate puzzles to unlock new areas and uncover the secrets of the nightmare.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f644e1e7a459169adb415262781f63aa.poster.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f644e1e7a459169adb415262781f63aa.webm?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f644e1e7a459169adb415262781f63aa.mp4?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/fae9ec246a5f95767c340d85be1a6c77.webp?t=1721570570\" width=283 height=24 /></span><br>Avoid and outsmart various malevolent entities that are determined to keep you trapped in the nightmare.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/5d98d61cc8342059cb866d1c99a3fee4.poster.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/5d98d61cc8342059cb866d1c99a3fee4.webm?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/5d98d61cc8342059cb866d1c99a3fee4.mp4?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/00a304673526bf86d6af1a04ab046ec6.webp?t=1721570570\" width=283 height=24 /></span><br>The deeper you go, the more the world reveals its twisted and horrifying nature. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f66e086857fe89b4b8cb26ffc5d47ecd.poster.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f66e086857fe89b4b8cb26ffc5d47ecd.webm?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f66e086857fe89b4b8cb26ffc5d47ecd.mp4?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>In Red Door Yellow Door, you'll explore an eerie, atmospheric world filled with hidden dangers and malevolent entities lurking in the shadows. As you navigate through this twisted reality, you'll need to find keys and solve puzzles to progress. Each door you open brings you closer to the ultimate goal: finding the elusive Red Yellow Door key that will allow you to wake up from this relentless nightmare. <br><br>Brace yourself for a journey into the unknown, where every choice you make could be your last. This is more than a game; it's a test of your courage and resolve.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/ac903bd4228f5954c83ccd0c8f3e6139.webp?t=1721570570\" width=450 height=24 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/45c013a8bb433e3b38d30ad12b003464.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=132 /></span><br>In Red Door Yellow Door, plunge into the depths of your mind, starting with what seems like a normal ritual but quickly revealing its sinister nature. Navigate eerie and haunting environments as you uncover the true essence of this mysterious practice. Confront your deepest fears, solve intricate puzzles, and evade malevolent entities on your quest to find the elusive Red Yellow Door—the only escape from this nightmare. Can you find the door and return to reality, or will you be trapped in the darkness forever?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/beea9c0aa45945c97d1dfc789b62daba.poster.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/beea9c0aa45945c97d1dfc789b62daba.webm?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/beea9c0aa45945c97d1dfc789b62daba.mp4?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f2ed96582c75d05058f4f3ad930f6d67.webp?t=1721570570\" width=283 height=24 /></span><br>Solve intricate puzzles to unlock new areas and uncover the secrets of the nightmare.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f644e1e7a459169adb415262781f63aa.poster.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.